  "text": "In this equation, Y is the predicted response surface function, β0 is a constant, βi is the slope or linear effect of the input variable, xii is the quadratic effect of input variable xi, and βij is the linear by linear interaction effect between the input variable xi and variable xj [CITATION_1] . ",
